---
// TODO: Replace decorative monogram panel with real shop interior photo when provided.
---
<section id="about" class="story" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
  <div class="container story__grid">
    <div class="story__copy" data-reveal>
      <span class="eyebrow">The Founder's Shop</span>
      <h2 id="story-heading">
        A brand built <span class="italic-accent">by barbers.</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        As seasoned barbers, we understand the confidence you gain after a
        fresh haircut. We aim to equip modern gentlemen with grooming
        essentials that ensure they feel and look their best — every single day.
      </p>

      <p>
        Modern Classic started in the chair. After more than ten years of
        cutting hair and watching clients struggle to recreate the style at
        home, our founder set out to build the products he wished his
        customers had: premium grooming essentials with no residue, no
        buildup, and a scent worth wearing.
      </p>

      <blockquote class="story__quote">
        <span class="story__quote-mark" aria-hidden="true">“</span>
        A great haircut should do more than look good for one day.
      </blockquote>

      <p>
        Today, MDRN Classic products are made by barbers, used in our shop,
        and shipped to clients across the country. The cut happens in
        Zanesville. The style stays with you wherever you go.
      </p>
    </div>

    <aside class="story__visual" aria-hidden="true" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 80ms">
      <div class="story__panel">
        <svg class="story__monogram" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" role="img"
             aria-label="MC monogram">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="mc-grad" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1">
              <stop offset="0%"  stop-color="#e6c785"/>
              <stop offset="55%" stop-color="#c9a35c"/>
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#8a6e35"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="92" stroke="url(#mc-grad)" stroke-width="1"/>
          <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="86" stroke="url(#mc-grad)" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.5"/>
          <text x="100" y="118" text-anchor="middle"
                font-family="Fraunces, Georgia, serif"
                font-size="92" font-weight="500"
                fill="url(#mc-grad)" letter-spacing="-2">MC</text>
          <g stroke="url(#mc-grad)" stroke-width="0.6" opacity="0.6">
            <line x1="100" y1="14" x2="100" y2="28"/>
            <line x1="100" y1="172" x2="100" y2="186"/>
            <line x1="14" y1="100" x2="28" y2="100"/>
            <line x1="172" y1="100" x2="186" y2="100"/>
          </g>
        </svg>

        <p class="story__caption">
          Est. Zanesville &nbsp;·&nbsp; Cut. Style. Shave.
        </p>

        <ul class="story__pillars">
          <li><strong>Cruelty-free</strong> formulations</li>
          <li><strong>Paraben-free</strong>, no buildup</li>
          <li><strong>Barber-tested</strong> in our chairs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story { background: var(--color-bg); }
  .story__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .story__copy { display: grid; gap: 1.1rem; max-width: 36rem; }
  .story__copy h2 { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .story__copy p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.06rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .story__quote {
    position: relative;
    margin: 1.25rem 0;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(201,163,92,0.05), transparent 60%);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144, 'SOFT' 80;
  }
  .story__quote-mark {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0.4rem;
    left: 0.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .story__visual { position: sticky; top: calc(var(--header-h) + 1.5rem); }
  .story__panel {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    align-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 35%, rgba(201,163,92,0.10), transparent 65%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-surface-2), var(--color-bg));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .story__panel::before {
    /* hairline frame */
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .story__panel::after {
    /* corner accent */
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,163,92,0.06), transparent 35%),
      linear-gradient(-45deg, rgba(201,163,92,0.04), transparent 35%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .story__monogram { width: min(70%, 280px); height: auto; }
  .story__caption {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.32em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .story__pillars {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.35rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  .story__pillars strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  @media (max-width: 860px) {
    .story__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .story__visual { position: static; max-width: 28rem; margin-inline: auto; }
  }
</style>
